  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8f\u0ba9\u0bcd - \u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Why fuel supply to health workers suspended - Ravikumuthes Vishanam",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Academy of Health Professionals, an organization of health professionals, has informed that the fuel supply to the health workers has been temporarily stopped on Friday as they will participate in the public protest tomorrow.",
        "He has accused the Secretary of the Ministry of Health, who has said that the strength of the protest movement cannot be reduced by such actions and has also mentioned that he is acting in a way to protect the government.",
        "The Secretary of the Ministry of Health has said that the activities of providing fuel to the health industry have been suspended for 48 hours.",
        "Ravikumuthes mentioned that as posts like Secretary of the Ministry of Health are politicized, people will lose faith in such posts and mentioned that their union will participate in the protest against the government tomorrow."
      ],
